body.name: PC Frame Test Bench ITX ATX MATX, Motherboard Case Frame Open Air Case Water Cooling Fan Chassis Test Bench Vertical Rack Computer Board Overclock Case Computer Mount Chassis (Black)
features: Fast Heat Dissipation: This chassis is fully open, the host installed on this chassis will quickly and timely dissipate the heat during operation, which can reduce the damage to the host and extend the life of the computer.

Great Durability: The chassis is made of very strong and durable 20 aluminum and thick acrylic plate, both of which are rust-resistant and sturdy. In addition, the metal frame is firmly fixed by screws, so it is very solid and stable.

Cool Look: This chassis looks very cool and beautiful. The black aluminum frame and the transparent acrylic panel make the chassis look like a product from futuristic technology. So placing it in the room will make the room look very cool and pretty.

Space-saving: The size of this chassis is 30*24.6*35.5cm/11.8*9.7*14inch, so it is very compact. So this chassis can be easily placed on or under a table. Compared to traditional chassis, it does not take up a lot of space.

Multiple Combinations: This chassis has two fan bays, one hard drive bay and one PCI bay. You can freely combine to install the host on this chassis in these bays according to your needs and preferences. This way you will have your own unique host.
body.description: DescriptionIs your computer mainframe too large and takes up too much space? Is your computer host dissipate heat slowly? Then you can try our open computer chassis. Our chassis is made of strong and durable aluminum and acrylic. The whole chassis is fully open without the casing, so it dissipates heat quickly.SpecificationColor: Black, Red OptionalChassis Material: 20x20 Aluminum Profile / Acrylic AccessoriesChassis Style: Bare Metal FrameApplicable Motherboard: For ITX Motherboard (17 *17cm/6.7*6.7inch) M-ATX, ATX MotherboardPower Supply Design: ATX Ordinary Power SupplyThermal Performance: Full Bare Heat DissipationChassis Assembly: DIY Self-AssemblySupport for Extended Hard Drive Positions: 1* 8.89cm/3.5inch, 1*6.35cm/ 2.5inchSupport PCI Expansion Slots: 7Switch Interface: Start / Restart Switch and IndicatorSize: 30*24.6*35.5cm/11.8*9.7*14inchWeight:1.8kg/4lbsDetailsMetal Switch Button: The switch on this chassis are all made of durable metal. We have also done a grinding and polishing process on the switch to make it look shiny and beautiful.High-quality Material: The chassis is made of very strong and durable 20 aluminum and thick acrylic plate, both of which are rust-resistant and sturdy.ApplicationIt is suitable for installing many kinds of desktop computer hosts. This chassis is suitable for Internet cafes, living rooms, study rooms, hotels, offices, etc.Package Included3* Metal Frames2* Acrylic Accessories1* Pair of Gloves1* Metal Switch1* Screw KitAll Accessories for InstallationNotesSome panels are designed for disassembly at one time, so start after considering and preparing.The motherboard is of size 305x244m and less.Regular maintenance of the acrylic panel will maintain the brightness of the original tear film for a long time.Please allow the slight color difference caused by the shooting light and 1-3 cm error due to manual measurement, and make sure you do not mind before ordering.
